Welcome to Gnusto's source directory.

The subdirectories here are:

frotz         - Patches to Frotz
gnusto        - The chrome for Gnusto installations: skin, locale
                and basic code
tests         - programs to test Gnusto
install.js    - The installation script for gnusto-*.xpi
tools         - Tools for debugging Gnusto
xpcom         - Gnusto's XPCOM components

Files in this directory:

Makefile      - makefile
README        - this file
